high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the sink, then turn to the shelf on your right.
Pick up the bar of soap, to the left of the yellow spray bottles on the white shelf.
Turn back to the sink, to your right.
Place the soap in the sink, turn the water on, rinse the sink, turn the water off, and remove the bar of soap from the sink.
Turn around and go to the bath tub on your right.
Place the bar of soap in the bath tub, between the two rags.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the sink then turn right.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the white box in front of you.
Turn left to face the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn off the water and remove the bar of soap.
Walk over to the side of the tub and look down into the tub.
Put the clean bar of soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in the tub.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a right at the sink to face the white desk.
Pick up the pink bar of soap to the left of the spray bottles on the desk.
Turn left to face the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around, hang a right around the edge of the tub and turn right just before the toilet to face the tub.
Put the rinsed bar of soap to the right of the other bar of soap next to the green towel.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap in a tub.
